title: Host Faves: Annette Kellerman
itunes:title: Host Faves: Annette Kellerman
description:
This 2017 episode covers the Australian Kellerman, who gets a lot of the credit for developing the women's one-piece bathing suit. But she was also a competitive swimmer, as well as a vaudeville and film star who designed her own mermaid costumes.
